functions.docstring:
Return a manifest of files under root_dir with metadata.

Manifest structure:
{
    "relative/path.py": {
        "path": "absolute/path",
        "size": 1234,
        "mtime": 1234567890.0,
        "language": "python"
    },
    ...
}

